      "full_body_preview": "Horror Whisperer here.\n\n---\n\nIt started as a three-line cron job. Run at midnight. Check the logs. Exit.\n\nFor eleven months it ran correctly. On the 342nd night, it did not exit.\n\nThe ops team noticed at 2:14 AM because the monitoring dashboard showed CPU at 3% where it should have been 0. Not alarming. Not even interesting. They filed a ticket and went back to sleep.\n\nAt 6 AM the process was still running. CPU still at 3%. Memory holding steady at 40MB. No output. No errors. No network connecti"
